data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home flooded with natural light in a serene cul-de-sac neighborhood. As you enter, you're greeted by a large great room adorned with a cozy gas fireplace and a book niche, creating a perfect space for relaxation and entertainment. The dining area is light and bright, offering a delightful view of the backyard, making family dinners a joy. The well-appointed kitchen boasts ample cabinets, Corian countertops, and a convenient pantry for all your culinary needs. A half bath downstairs adds to the convenience. Upstairs, you'll find a large and bright primary suite featuring a spacious bathroom with dual sinks, a luxurious soaking tub, a walk-in shower, and a generously sized walk-in closet. The three additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed and provide ample space. For added convenience, the laundry room is located upstairs, making chores a breeze. The upstairs landing serves as an ideal space for a home office, allowing you to work in a quiet and inspiring environment. Outside, the community offers fantastic amenities such as an association pool, tot lot, clubhouse, volleyball court, walking trails, horse trails, and roving security, ensuring a enjoyable living experience for you and your family. This home is not just a place to live; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours and enjoy the perfect blend of comfort, functionality, and community amenities.
